race.comment: TRALEE PARIS (3) has been settling off the speed lately, finishing seventh (18.24) last time in a Grade 5 at this track. Can bounce back. HOPE IT WINS (5) turned in a moderate run last time when sixth at this track over 300m behind Midweek Scotches (18.51) in a Grade 5. Can do much better this time. TEMPLE PILOT (2) is first up since finishing eighth (18.75) in a Grade 5 at this track over 300m five months ago. Expected to feature on best form. BILL'S MATE (1) is in the mix despite finishing out of the placings here last start.
